arStrings.szText: Casting {c_important}Dash{/c} increases your Critical Strike Chance by {c_number}[{SF_29}*100|%+|]{/c} for {c_number}{SF_34}{/c} seconds.
At the end of {c_important}Dash{/c} , Knock Down surrounding enemies for {c_number}{SF_12}{/c} seconds and deal {c_number}[{SF_28}*100|x%|]{/c} of its damage to them.
{c_important}Dash{/c} has {c_number}{SF_16}{/c} additional Charge and its Charge Cooldown is reduced by {c_number}{SF_17}{/c} seconds.
